---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import { buttonVariants } from '@/components/ui/button'
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import logo from '../assets/logo.svg'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="PRI5M Process"
  description="Modern development for forward thinking individuals"
>

<section class="gap-6pb-40 md:py-100 container grid items-left pt-10">
  <div class="pb-40 pt-20">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-2 max-w-[700px] md:w-full text-left">
      <h1
        class="animate-fade text-4xl font-extrabold animate-delay-200 md:text-6xl"
      >
      Design. Build. Ship.
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-md mt-10 animate-fade text-muted-foreground animate-delay-300 md:text-lg"
      >
Whether you’re starting from scratch, or levelling-up an existing product suite, we bring experience and pragmatism that moves the needle on real business goals.</p>

<p
class="text-md mb-10 mt-5 animate-fade text-muted-foreground animate-delay-300 md:text-lg"
>
We’re experts at React, Next.js, Astro, and GraphQL. We’re internationally recognised for our work in design systems, content management systems, and front-end infrastructure. We sweat team productivity and practices. And we’d love to hear from you.</p>
      </p>
      
      <div
      class="flex animate-fade-down justify-left gap-4 animate-delay-200 animate-duration-[800ms] max-[600px]:flex-col"
    >
      <a
        href="/process"
        rel="noreferrer"
        class={buttonVariants({ variant: 'fadeintro' })}
      >
        Learn our Process
      </a>
      <a
        href="/survey"
        rel="noreferrer"
        class={buttonVariants({ variant: 'outlineintro' })}
        ><Image
          src={logo}
          alt="PRI5M Logo"
          id="site-logo"
          class="mr-3 max-w-[24px]"
        />
         Take our Survey
      </a>
    </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
